This paper discusses the use of intelligent systems to improve data sharing and compliance with governance rules. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybersecurity and privacy (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), and software engineering (cs.SE).
